<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ز م هـ ر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٣٤٦ - ز م هـ ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ازمهرَّ يزمهرّ، ازمهرِرْ/ ازْمهِرَّ، ازمهرارًا، فهو مُزمهِرّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ازمهرَّتِ العينُ:</span> زَمْهرت، احمرّت من الغضب.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• ازمهرَّ اليومُ:</span> اشتدّ بردُه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• ازمهرَّ وجهُه:</span> كلَح وعبَس.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>